{"tid":1176324,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"6月9號 你有咩做？","createTime":"2019-05-29T06:49:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-29T06:54:09.000Z","uid":123163,"like":5,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"163b153ee6c3aca4609a9bb2ed8af61f5c823f9d","tid":1176324,"uid":123163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T06:49:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">6月9號 記得上街！<br />\n6月9號 記得上街！<br />\n6月9號 記得上街！</span></span><br />\n重要野要講三次<br />\n<br />\n逃犯條例影響緊每一個香港人 包括睇緊呢個msg嘅你<br />\n新聞網媒嘅資訊睇唔明 覺得唔關你事<br />\n其實好簡單<br />\n條例入面其中一項<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">香港居民在香港觸犯涉及危害國家安全罪行</span><br />\n係會<span style=\"font-size: large;\">被送中</span><br />\n而大家都好清楚 係大陸嘅角度來講<br />\n講句野 寫段文 開下遮<br />\n都可以係危害國家安全<br />\n所以 逃犯條例嘅通過 就姐係剝削香港人言論自由<br />\n<br />\n因此我係到再次呼籲 作為香港人嘅你<br />\n6月9日 上街 守護作為香港人嘅核心價值<br />\n一齊守護呢個我地會稱為屋企嘅地方&mdash;&mdash;香港"},{"pid":"2a60ef06dd80e120e9eea6ea9f9828d1e925f655","tid":1176324,"uid":104833,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T06:51:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>毒撚們唔好覺得少自己一個唔少 記得出黎 we need </strong></span>"},{"pid":"dff77b712f98b75bfced237b8e559abc73c24671","tid":1176324,"uid":104833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a60ef06dd80e120e9eea6ea9f9828d1e925f655","tid":1176324,"uid":104833,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T06:51:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>毒撚們唔好覺得少自己一個唔少 記得出黎 we need </strong></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T06:51:46.000Z","msg":"少左個u字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b150ba9a22877ca9f99328d35ce67188e96e5f01","tid":1176324,"uid":123163,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-2